@startuml CD-02-ProjektyRizika
skinparam roundcorner 5

object "Manager" as User
object "Livewire\nKomponenta" as LW
object "Controller" as Ctrl
object "Model\n(Project / Risk)" as Model
object "SQLite DB" as DB

User --> LW : 1: Akce uživatele (klik, vyplnění formuláře)
LW --> Ctrl : 2: Livewire Action (store / update / delete)
Ctrl --> Model : 3: Eloquent dotaz (create / find / update)
Model --> DB : 4: SQL dotaz
DB --> Model : 5: výsledek
Model --> Ctrl : 6: objekt / kolekce
Ctrl --> LW : 7: aktualizace stavu
LW --> User : 8: re-render UI (bez page refresh)

@enduml
